Goblin Wrangler

2 HP, 3 AP, 2MP, 1 pdef, 0mdef

Bite: 2 AP: 1pP+1

Lash: 3 AP: During its next turn, target troll gets 2 additional dice on its first attack

Cower: 2 AP:  Move from any position next to a troll to any other position adjacent to the same 
              troll without provoking AO
              
Type: Goblin
